x solid rgba(0,0,0,.25);padding:8px 0;color:var(--color-text);outline:none;width:110px;' /></div><button type='button' class='il-btn' id='il-filter-submit'><span>Search Listings</span></button></div></div><p style='font-family:var(--font-label);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(0,0,0,.25);text-align:center;padding:8px;margin:0;'>[ Wire filter functionality to WP_Query or plugin (FacetWP, SearchWP) in Phase 2 ]</p>"
